STEP 1 -------------
*Open a terminal in the directory where the zip file is located and copy-paste :

>>>
UUID="Lockscreen42-LMAYSASH"
unzip Desktop/Lockscreen42-LMAYSASH.zip -d ~/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions/$UUID
mkdir -p ~/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions/$UUID
cp metadata.json extension.js ~/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions/$UUID/
>>>

STEP 2 -------------
*Log out
*Log in
*copy-paste the following in a terminal :

>>>
gnome-extensions enable Lockscreen42-LMAYSASH
>>>
